snippet.title: Bottle Flip 3D
snippet.description:
IOS - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bottle-flip-3d/id1447504309?ls=1&mt=8

Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=pampam.ibf2

You have to flip a plastic bottle in the exciting arcade game Bottle Flip 3D! Make the bottle jump or even double flip. How? Just tap the screen at the right moment and jump!
